2011-03-08T06:31:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-08/south-african-daybook-old-mutual-swings-to-profit-africa-economic-forum.html
  Old Mutual Plc (OML) , the largest insurer
in  Africa , may swing to a full-year profit after a rebound in
equity markets. The company may post earnings per share of
15.4 pence according to the median estimate of 10 analysts
surveyed by Bloomberg. 